sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route / LB<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP TLS Terminate
    participant EnvoyF as EnvoyFilter<br/>ext_authz
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth /<br/>OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Upstream as Upstream Component<br/>(Dashboard, Registry, etc.)

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 1: Gateway Authentication (OAuth/OIDC)

    Client->>Route: HTTPS Request (443/TCP)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Route->>Gateway: Re-encrypt / Passthrough
    Gateway->>EnvoyF: Request interception
    EnvoyF->>AuthProxy: ext_authz check (8443/TCP)<br/>HTTPS, TLS (service-ca)
    AuthProxy->>OAuth: OAuth2/OIDC auth (443/TCP)<br/>HTTPS, TLS 1.2+<br/>Client credentials
    OAuth-->>AuthProxy: Token / Auth response
    AuthProxy-->>EnvoyF: Allow/Deny + headers
    EnvoyF-->>Gateway: Authorized request
    Gateway->>Upstream: Forward with Bearer Token<br/>(Lua filter injects access token)
    Upstream-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 2: Component Lifecycle (DSC → Component)

    participant Admin as Cluster Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as DSC Webhook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller
    participant CompCtrl as Component Controller
    participant Manifests as Kustomize Manifests<br/>(filesystem)

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create/Update DSC CR<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission Review (443/TCP)<br/>HTTPS, Webhook client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated (singleton check,<br/>Kueue guard, v1/v2 migration)
    K8sAPI-->>Admin: CR Created
    K8sAPI->>DSCCtrl: Watch event
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Component CR<br/>(e.g., Kserve, Dashboard)<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>CompCtrl: Watch event
    CompCtrl->>Manifests: Render kustomize
    Manifests-->>CompCtrl: Rendered resources
    CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply manifests (6443/TCP)<br/>HTTPS, ServiceAccount token
    CompCtrl-->>DSCCtrl: Status update

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 3: Dashboard Redirect (Legacy URL)

    participant LegacyClient as Client (legacy URL)
    participant LegacyRoute as OpenShift Route<br/>(legacy hostname)<br/>443/TCP Edge TLS
    participant Nginx as dashboard-redirect nginx<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant NewGateway as Gateway (new hostname)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    LegacyClient->>LegacyRoute: HTTPS (443/TCP)<br/>Edge termination
    LegacyRoute->>Nginx: HTTP (8080/TCP)<br/>No encryption
    Nginx-->>LegacyClient: HTTP 301 Redirect<br/>→ new gateway hostname
    LegacyClient->>NewGateway: HTTPS (443/TCP)<br/>TLS Terminate → OAuth/OIDC flow
